How To Run

1. Open the bash file and set the configuration parameters

2. Give running permissions to the bash file by typing the following command

chmod +x main.sh

3. Now run the bash file by typing the following command

./main.sh

It should open 4 terminals:

1. signal
2. log
3. server
4. client

If it doesnt open all the 4 terminals, please run the bash file again.

